item.title: CVE-2019-4651|2024-08-04T19:40:48.258Z -- ibm -- jazz%20reporting%20service%20%28jrs%29
item.description: IBM Jazz Reporting Service (JRS) 6.0.6.1 is vulnerable to SQL injection. A remote attacker could send specially-crafted SQL statements, which could allow the attacker to view, add, modify or delete information in the back-end database. IBM X-Force ID: 170962.
